G fight: The Best of Women's Mixed Martial Arts DVD is best as title represent.  You will not regret purchase it, so just sit back and watch.  Women MMA is fast pase none-stop action in every seconds, so you must keep eye on screen or you will miss exciting fight of women's MMA.  Also I will recommend Hook N Fight Revolution series.
